data.title: Convert German Marks (DEM) and New Taiwan Dollars (TWD): Currency Exchange Rate Conversion Calculator
data.meta_description: Calculator to convert money in German Mark (DEM) to and from New Taiwan Dollar (TWD) using up to date exchange rates.
data.text:
This German Mark and New Taiwan Dollar convertor is up to date with exchange rates from August 17, 2024.

Enter the amount to be converted in the box to the left of German Mark. Use "Swap currencies" to make New Taiwan Dollar the default currency. Click on New Taiwan Dollars or German Marks to convert between that currency and all other currencies.

The German Mark is the currency in Germany (DE, DEU). The New Taiwan Dollar is the currency in Taiwan (TW, TWN). The German Mark is also known as Deutschmark, and Deutsche Mark. The New Taiwan Dollar is also known as the Taiwanese Dollar. The symbol for TWD can be written NT$, NTD, and NT. The New Taiwan Dollar is divided into 100 cents. The exchange rate for the German Mark was last updated on August 15, 2024 from The International Monetary Fund. The exchange rate for the New Taiwan Dollar was last updated on June 5, 2023 from MSN. The DEM conversion factor has 6 significant digits. The TWD conversion factor has 5 significant digits.
